These are Puzzles for 7x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 7x4-Level-2-1::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: tea, juice, soy-milk, mirinda
There 4 different types of food: garlic, papaya, strawberry, avocado
The people have 4 different hobbies: drawing, gardening, sudoku, reading
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: classical, r&b, salsa, ambient
4 different pets are kept: guinea-pig, ferret, horse, hamster
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: golf, handball, skateboarding, weightlifting
The people use 4 different means of transport: boat, car, train, ship
 1. the person eating garlic is between the person drinking tea and the owner of the guinea-pig##2
 2. the person eating strawberry is on the far left##1
 3. the person driving the ship is on the left of the fan of classical##1
 4. the owner of the ferret is on the right of the person who's sport is handball##1
 5. the person driving the train is on the right of the person drinking juice##1
 6. the person eating papaya is on the right of the person who's hobby is gardening##1
 7. the fan of r&b is between the person driving the car and the owner of the hamster##2
 8. the person driving the car is on the left of the person who's hobby is drawing##1
 9. the person eating avocado is the fan of classical##1
10. the person who's sport is handball is the person eating papaya##1
11. the person who's sport is weightlifting is the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
12. the person who's hobby is reading is on the right of the person drinking soy-milk##1
13. the owner of the horse is on the left of the person who's hobby is reading##1
14. the person eating avocado is on the right of the person who's sport is skateboarding##1
15. the fan of salsa is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |       3       |     4      |
| Beverage      | soy-milk        | mirinda     | juice | tea      |
| Food          | strawberry | papaya    | garlic      | avocado  |
| Hobby         | gardening  | reading    | drawing       | sudoku     |
| Music-Genre   | salsa        | ambient       | r&b          | classical |
| Pet           | horse    | guinea-pig | ferret      | hamster     |
| Sport         | golf   | handball   | skateboarding      | weightlifting    |
| Transport     | boat        | car        | ship    | train    |

