 7. the owner of the chinchilla is on the left of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
 8. the person eating pear is the person driving the snowmobile##1
 9. the person driving the skateboard is the person who's hobby is traveling##1
10. the person eating apricot is on the right of the person drinking tea##1
11. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the left of the owner of the snake##1
